head.note:
In English and Albanian;
                                    Albanian text not printed. Ratification advised by the Senate,
                                    February 6, 1935; ratified by the President, March 13, 1935;
                                    ratified by Albania, April 12, 1935; ratifications exchanged at
                                    Tirana, July 22, 1935; proclaimed by the President, July 29,
                                    1935.
